{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Change P.I.P (Personal Independence Payment) back to DLA.",
        "additional_details": "DLA was helpful towards those with challenging needs, such as, Diabetes, mental health troubles, cystic fibrosis and every other Disability, the money that DLA gave to those people helped them live and thrive until it changed to PIP ( personal independence payment). With pip introduced back a few years ago it has been classed as extremely hard to achieve within the claims that people have, they don\u2019t tell you to bring evidence such as doctors letters or a specialist letter.",
        "background": "Personal independence payment is extremely hard to achieve if you have an illness/disability such as Cancer, Diabetes,cystic fibrosis and other challenging disabilities, the country used to have a system called DLA (Disability Living Allowance) which helped those With those Disability\u2019s live &thrive",
